
Ranger Help for: carve arrow
============================

SYNTAX:      carve arrow/carve bolt
USAGE:       forest,jungle,swamp
SLOT COST:   5
BASE SP:     10 sp
SKILL TYPE:  arrow

SUMMARY:    
This skill allows a Ranger to carve an arrow or bolt from wooded areas.
Arrows are used in shortbows and longbows, while bolts are used in
crossbows. Once carved, arrows and bolts can be enhanced by fire,
poison and other methods, if they Ranger knows how to. The Ranger must
have a slash type weapon in order to cut and carve the wood.

